             was indicted for that <rs id="t18100718-64-off380" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18100718-64-off380" type="offenceCategory" value="sexual"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18100718-64-off380" type="offenceSubcategory" value="bigamy"></interp>
               he<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181007180044"></xptr>on the <rs id="t18100718-64-cd381" type="crimeDate">5th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100718-64-off380 t18100718-64-cd381"></join> last, feloniously took to wife one 
                     
                        <persName id="t18100718-64-victim649" type="victimName">
                           Sarah 
                           Morris
                        <interp inst="t18100718-64-victim649" type="surname" value="Morris"></interp>
